# The Kaini/Bocuma voice — corrected to the community's actual
# SH-01A panel reading, which is humbler than every guess:
#   SAW ONLY, full level. No pulse, no sub, no noise.
# The identity is the ENVELOPE and FILTER, not the mix:
#   - one fast-attack / LONG-decay / near-zero-sustain contour
#     shaping both loudness and cutoff (the 101 shares one ADSR):
#     every note is a bloom that fades, never a held organ tone
#   - strong key tracking (KYBD ~8/10) on the OTA-cascade filter
#     (circuit 1 — the IR3109's family), moderate-low resonance
#   - light triangle vibrato, and AUTO portamento at almost minimum
#     time: the fast linear legato glide
# Wow, tape, and room live in the song / preset bus lines below.
